	   <tr><td colspan=2>I haven't played a Rogue in a long time so I hope that people will correct me if I'm wrong, but you used to be able to use the Pick Lock Skill on the boats. Not only was a great way to pass the boring time on the boats, but there used to be a Bug that would allow you to speed up the boat when you used Pick Lock on it. This resulted in boats nearly passing one another, and it was later fixed. I'm not sure if they nerfed the ability to practice Pick Locks on the boat at the same time.<br>&nbsp;<br>________<br><br>I've travelled this world and have seen many wondrous things. You are not one of them.</td></tr>
