	   <tr><td colspan=2>At seventh level, the absolute best place to solo is misty thicket.&nbsp;&nbsp;Kill bats and occasional wasps over and over, and you will find yourself at rank 9 before you know it.  It is one of the best kept secrets in the game.  Also, keep all your bat wings and sell them to magic users for a few pp a stack.  Its one of their components.  You probably should not bother trying to group until you have backstab at 10, anyways.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
