	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.55]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Pickpocketing USED not to affect what is on the mob.<br><br>It has been CHANGED so that NOW it DOES come from the groups loot.<br><br>There is no guarrantee that you will get all the loot on the first go of course. You also can't loot the last of any type of coin (maybe not last item either not sure). <br>Getting 1pp 1gp 1sp and 1cp is the most common giveaway for a group. There is an art to PPing&nbsp;&nbsp;take your cut but don't get too greedy and tip off the group.<br>If you're feeling really sneaky you can also do something blatantly honest or generous to divert attention ;)<br><br>Once you get high enough you can do sow-by picking from merchants and high lvl mobs. Then you're stealing from someone elses group.. nothing wrong with that.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
