	   <tr><td colspan=2>Depends on whether you are playing with or without the ability to injure/be injured by other players.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you follow the ways of discord you can pickpocket from other players otherwise you can't.  As for who is better it really depends on what the player is carrying and your skill level.  The better your skill level the more interesting the "find" potential.  At level 7 you will be lucky to get a few coppers or a silver.  Find a group camping a spawn site when you are soloing and pick the MOBS as they duke it out with the campers.  It was a great way to increase my skill without a whole lot of risk (make sure you use your stealth skills too...makes you less appetizing to suddenly popping mobs).<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
