	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am still relatively new to EQ (my main is a Level 10 cleric). As you know clerics drain money quickly so I wanted to create a 2nd character #1 just for fun (being a high elf cleric who lives to save lives gets a little dull after a while) and #2 to supplement my income (which I understand a rogue is good at).&nbsp;&nbsp;To add a little RP I thought a dark elf rogue would be a nice counter to a high elf cleric but I keep hearing the horror stories about being a DE.  Is there a REALLY good guide out there for DEs?  Like a survival guide?  And if there are any experienced DE rogues out there, could you give me some advice on getting started and staying alive?  Thanks for your help!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
